# Normalize line endings. Store text as LF in the repo and check it out as LF on
# every platform - this overrides a local core.autocrlf=true, so Windows
# checkouts no longer get CRLF working copies that trip prettier's
# endOfLine:"lf" check (CI runs on Linux and never saw this, hence the skew).
# Git auto-detects text vs binary; the entries below just pin the known binaries.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets - never normalize or diff as text. (SVG is XML, left as text.)
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
